{"type":"message","id":"e5426b47","parentId":"97f1d395","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:11:29.032Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 7:11 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-22 23:11 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774221089028}}
