{"type":"message","id":"16d6320d","parentId":"c0366f17","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:24:09.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - queries 1 works (TemporalOnly → TemporalAttentionStore). Queries 2 and 3 return 0 results.\n\nFor \"what does TemporalAttentionStore affect?\" — the entity resolves to the class but query_impact might return 0 because the static analyzer doesn't capture method-level call relationships well.\n\nFor \"what uses Window?\" — `Window` might not resolve to anything specific.\n\nLet me check what's happening with these:","thinkingSignature":"fbbb8f3e75e3ecef0a6c73c1a9f4b35ca6e941c705bbd333ea8cba4faa3c1ab5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9npbop5dh86k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:/dev/code-cause && python -c \"\nimport sys; sys.path.insert(0, 'src')\nfrom causal_indexer import StaticAnalyzer, CausalGraph, QueryEngine\n\nanalyzer = StaticAnalyzer('C:/dev/temporal-attention')\nanalyzer.analyze()\ngraph = CausalGraph.from_analysis(analyzer.definitions, analyzer.references)\nengine = QueryEngine(graph)\n\n# Debug TemporalAttentionStore\nq = 'what does TemporalAttentionStore affect'\ne = engine._extract_entity(q.lower())\nr = engine._resolve_entity(e)\nprint('Extracted:', e, 'Resolved:', r)\nif r:\n    imp = graph.query_impact(r, depth=5)\n    print('Impacts:', len(imp), [i['name'] for i in imp[:5]])\n\n# Debug Window  \nq2 = 'what uses Window'\ne2 = engine._extract_entity(q2.lower())\nr2 = engine._resolve_entity(e2)\nprint('Extracted:', e2, 'Resolved:', r2)\nif r2:\n    imp2 = graph.query_impact(r2, depth=5)\n    print('Impacts:', len(imp2))\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":31005,"output":357,"cacheRead":12619,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43981,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774221842979}}
